name: Order inventory items test
description: Verification of the inventory order options

testStage.description: Verification of the inventory order options

steps.name: Login with valid user
Send 'standard_user' to Username
Send 'secret_sauce' to Password
Click on login-button
Sort items by visible text: Name (Z to A)
Select 'Name (Z to A)' from product_sort_container

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare Z to A item list with initial item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Backpack] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]
Sort items by visible text: Price (low to high)
Select 'Price (low to high)' from product_sort_container

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare Low to High item list with initial item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare Low to High item list with Z to A item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket] - Initial list: [Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Backpack]
Sort items by visible text: Price (high to low)
Select 'Price (high to low)' from product_sort_container

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare High to Low item list with initial item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Onesie] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare High to Low item list with Z to A item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Onesie] - Initial list: [Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Backpack]

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare High to Low item list with Low to High item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Onesie] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket]
Sort items by visible text: Name (A to Z)
Select 'Name (A to Z)' from product_sort_container

Assertion Is Equal To: Compare A to Z item list with initial item list and check that they are equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)]

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare A to Z item list with Z to A item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Backpack]

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare A to Z item list with Low to High item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Onesie, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket]

Assertion Is Not Equal To: Compare A to Z item list with High to Low item list and check that they are not equal - Actual list: [Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Onesie, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red)] - Initial list: [Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket, Sauce Labs Backpack, Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt, Test.allTheThings() T-Shirt (Red), Sauce Labs Bike Light, Sauce Labs Onesie]
